<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 14:06:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>伊朗禁止向儿童教授外语</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-bans-teaching-foreign-languages-to-kids/articleshow/104501351.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104501351.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗已禁止在幼儿园和小学教授所有外语，包括英语和阿拉伯语。该禁令旨在保护年轻儿童的伊朗身份。波斯语是伊朗的官方语言，受到阿拉伯语的影响，但也融入了法语和英语的元素。此举是继2018年禁止小学教授英语之后做出的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 13:05:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-bans-teaching-foreign-languages-to-kids/articleshow/104501351.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国难民事务高级专员表示，在其他世界危机期间，决不能忘记逃离缅甸的罗兴亚人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/un-refugee-chief-says-rohingya-who-fled-myanmar-must-not-be-forgotten-during-other-world-crises/articleshow/104499080.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104499080.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国难民事务高级专员呼吁为来自缅甸的罗兴亚难民提供更多支持，强调有必要在其他全球危机中解决他们的困境。专员强调了由于缅甸持续冲突和资金减少而提供人道主义援助面临的挑战。虽然自愿返回缅甸是首选解决方案，但仍有重大挑战需要克服。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 11:41:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/un-refugee-chief-says-rohingya-who-fled-myanmar-must-not-be-forgotten-during-other-world-crises/articleshow/104499080.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦动荡的俾路支省发生手榴弹爆炸，造成儿童死亡、8人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/child-killed-8-injured-in-hand-grenade-explosion-in-pakistans-restive-balochistan/articleshow/104496787.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104496787.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一枚手榴弹在巴基斯坦俾路支省爆炸，造成一名儿童死亡、八人受伤。据警方称，手榴弹爆炸时，一些孩子正在玩手榴弹。伤者立即被送往医院。瓦德的DSP表示，这并不是第一次发生此类事件。武装分子和分裂分子留下或投下此类危险的爆炸物。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 11:35:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/child-killed-8-injured-in-hand-grenade-explosion-in-pakistans-restive-balochistan/articleshow/104496787.cms</guid></item><item><title>犹太学生在巴黎墙壁上贴满据信被哈马斯扣为人质的法国公民的照片</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/jewish-students-plaster-paris-walls-with-photos-of-french-citizens-believed-held-hostage-by-hamas/articleshow/104497298.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104497298.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国主要的犹太学生联盟在巴黎各地张贴了海报，上面画着据信在与以色列的战争中被哈马斯扣为人质的法国公民的面孔。海报顶部的红色横幅上写着“绑架”字样。法国犹太学生会敦促人们声援人质，并强调这不仅是犹太社区的问题，也是对自由和民主的攻击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 10:50:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/jewish-students-plaster-paris-walls-with-photos-of-french-citizens-believed-held-hostage-by-hamas/articleshow/104497298.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯迈出废除核试验条约批准的第一步</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-duma-passes-first-step-to-scrap-ratification-of-nuclear-test-ban-treaty/articleshow/104495992.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104495992.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯议会周二迈出了撤销对《全面禁止核试验条约》批准的第一步，并指责一位高级议员所说的美国对全球安全不负责任的态度。议会下议院杜马以 412 票对零票、无弃权票在三读中的第一次投票中批准撤销批准书。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 10:24:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-duma-passes-first-step-to-scrap-ratification-of-nuclear-test-ban-treaty/articleshow/104495992.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普将再次访问纽约法院进行正在进行的欺诈审判</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-to-visit-nyc-court-again-in-ongoing-fraud-trial/articleshow/104500651.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104500651.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普证实，他将出席曼哈顿法院对纽约总检察长利蒂西亚·詹姆斯对其提起的 2.5 亿美元诉讼的审判。特朗普批评这位法官高度政治化，并指责法律体系腐败和破坏。该案件指控特朗普在财务文件上夸大了自己的净资产，以获得优惠的贷款条件。特朗普的出庭最初与他的前律师迈克尔·科恩的预期证词一致，但科恩的证词由于医疗原因而被推迟。特朗普称这次审判是出于政治动机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 12:27:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-to-visit-nyc-court-again-in-ongoing-fraud-trial/articleshow/104500651.cms</guid></item><item><title>蒂姆·斯科特赞扬以色列内塔尼亚胡的“克制”，称美国应向该地区调动更多火力</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/tim-scott-praises-restraint-of-israels-netanyahu-says-us-should-move-more-firepower-to-region/articleshow/104496003.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104496003.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;参议员蒂姆·斯科特赞扬以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡对哈马斯最近的袭击表现出克制和耐心。斯科特强调美国与以色列并肩站在一起的重要性，并批评唐纳德·特朗普对内塔尼亚胡的评论。他还呼吁美国增加火力，准备营救加沙的美国人质。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 10:29:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/tim-scott-praises-restraint-of-israels-netanyahu-says-us-should-move-more-firepower-to-region/articleshow/104496003.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京和欧尔班在国际紧张局势中重申俄匈关系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-and-orban-reaffirm-russian-hungarian-ties-amid-international-strains/articleshow/104496126.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104496126.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 10:29:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-and-orban-reaffirm-russian-hungarian-ties-amid-international-strains/articleshow/104496126.cms</guid></item><item><title>习近平应对国内挑战，中国外交趋软</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/softer-china-diplomacy-as-xi-navigates-challenges-at-home/articleshow/104495631.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104495631.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国一直对世界采取更加温和的态度，从监狱中释放了一名澳大利亚记者，邀请美国军方参加国防论坛，并重组了与斯里兰卡和赞比亚的债务协议。这一语气的转变旨在安抚外国投资者，并反驳中国“一带一路”倡议是“债务陷阱外交”的观点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 10:09:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/softer-china-diplomacy-as-xi-navigates-challenges-at-home/articleshow/104495631.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国：以色列的加沙撤离令可能违反国际法</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-gaza-evacuation-order-could-breach-international-law-un/articleshow/104494931.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104494931.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国人权办公室表示担心，以色列对加沙的围困及其飞地北部的疏散令可能构成强制转移平民，这将违反国际法。该办公室表示，以色列没有做出足够的努力，为撤离的平民提供适当的住宿、卫生、健康、安全和营养。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 09:50:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-gaza-evacuation-order-could-breach-international-law-un/articleshow/104494931.cms</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩发射反坦克导弹后，黎以边境再次爆发冲突</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/clashes-again-erupt-on-the-lebanon-israel-border-after-an-anti-tank-missile-is-fired-from-lebanon/articleshow/104494601.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104494601.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周二，黎巴嫩和以色列边境再次爆发冲突，自最近加沙战争爆发以来，以色列军队和黎巴嫩武装团体发生了一系列小规模冲突。据萨法德齐夫医疗中心称，一枚从黎巴嫩发射的反坦克导弹周二上午落在以色列北部的梅图拉镇，造成三人受伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 09:39:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/clashes-again-erupt-on-the-lebanon-israel-border-after-an-anti-tank-missile-is-fired-from-lebanon/articleshow/104494601.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯总统普京在中国与匈牙利总统欧尔班举行会谈</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russias-putin-holds-talks-with-hungarys-orban-in-china/articleshow/104493898.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104493898.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京在华会见匈牙利总理欧尔班，并就与匈牙利等欧洲国家保持和发展关系的重要性进行了会谈。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 09:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russias-putin-holds-talks-with-hungarys-orban-in-china/articleshow/104493898.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普介入以色列对哈马斯的战争，誓言禁止加沙难民进入美国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-weighs-in-on-israels-war-on-hamas-vows-to-ban-gaza-refugees-from-entering-us/articleshow/104494710.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104494710.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将把对难民的冻结扩大到包括来自加沙的人。他表达了反移民立场，并提出了各种限制移民和难民数量的政策。特朗普还发誓要禁止来自世界某些地区的个人，特别是信奉伊斯兰教的地区，并提议根据移民的意识形态来筛选移民。他没有提供有关如何执行此类筛查的详细信息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 09:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-weighs-in-on-israels-war-on-hamas-vows-to-ban-gaza-refugees-from-entering-us/articleshow/104494710.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登前往以色列和约旦，重点关注地面进攻和人道主义危机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-heading-to-israel-and-jordan-focused-on-ground-offensive-and-humanitarian-crisis/articleshow/104494425.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104494425.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统乔·拜登即将前往以色列和约旦，评估以色列在与哈马斯冲突中的目标，并强调向加沙提供人道主义援助的重要性。访问期间，拜登将与以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡以及约旦、埃及和巴勒斯坦领导人会面。此行的目的是表达对以色列的声援，同时避免更广泛的地区战争并解决加沙的人道主义危机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 09:34:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-heading-to-israel-and-jordan-focused-on-ground-offensive-and-humanitarian-crisis/articleshow/104494425.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平在会谈中宣扬与智利的密切关系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-xi-jinping-touts-close-relationship-with-chile-in-talks/articleshow/104493915.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104493915.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国国家主席习近平周二在北京会见智利总统博里奇时表示，智利始终走在中国同拉美和加勒比国家关系前列。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 09:20:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-xi-jinping-touts-close-relationship-with-chile-in-talks/articleshow/104493915.cms</guid></item><item><title>“咄咄逼人”的中国战斗机惊扰了加拿大飞机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/aggressive-chinese-fighter-jets-spook-canadian-plane-on-un-mission/articleshow/104491668.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104491668.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名加拿大将军批评中国空军对中国海岸附近的加拿大侦察机采取攻击性和不安全的行为。这起事件涉及一架中国战斗机拦截巡逻机，向其飞行路径投掷照明弹，并在距离飞机5米的范围内飞行。中国就此事件向加拿大提出外交申诉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 08:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/aggressive-chinese-fighter-jets-spook-canadian-plane-on-un-mission/articleshow/104491668.cms</guid></item><item><title>议长：俄罗斯将撤销对禁止核试验条约的批准</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-is-revoking-ratification-of-nuclear-test-ban-treaty-parliament-speaker/articleshow/104485973.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104485973.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯议会议长表示，由于美国对全球安全采取不负责任的态度，俄罗斯将撤回对《全面禁止核试验条约》的批准。弗拉基米尔·普京总统此前曾建议撤销批准，因为美国尚未批准该条约。俄罗斯仍将是禁试条约签署国，并将继续与禁试条约组织和全球监测系统合作。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 05:16:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-is-revoking-ratification-of-nuclear-test-ban-treaty-parliament-speaker/articleshow/104485973.cms</guid></item><item><title>“我是真主的战士”：受伊斯兰国启发的枪手在布鲁塞尔杀死了两名瑞典人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/i-am-fighter-for-allah-isis-inspired-gunman-kills-2-swedes-in-brussels/articleshow/104484105.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104484105.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名自称效忠伊斯兰国的枪手在布鲁塞尔杀害了两人，比利时警方在全市范围内展开搜捕。在比利时对阵瑞典的 2024 年欧洲杯预选赛之前，袭击者在伊普尔大道附近的一辆出租车中向一群瑞典球迷开枪，该大道距离该市著名的大广场以北仅几分钟路程。旁观者拍摄的令人不安的视频显示，袭击者骑着摩托车在公共场合跟踪并向人们开枪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 04:08:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/i-am-fighter-for-allah-isis-inspired-gunman-kills-2-swedes-in-brussels/articleshow/104484105.cms</guid></item><item><title>经过十年的大项目和巨额债务，中国的“一带一路”正在发生怎样的变化</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/how-chinas-belt-and-road-initiative-is-changing-after-a-decade-of-big-projects-and-big-debts/articleshow/104484292.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104484292.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着中国寻求解决债务和环境问题，中国的“一带一路”倡议将变得更小、更环保。 “一带一路”倡议旨在促进贸易、深化中国的全球关系，带动了全球重大基础设施项目的建设。然而，这一举措也导致了巨额债务和环境批评。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 04:02:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/how-chinas-belt-and-road-initiative-is-changing-after-a-decade-of-big-projects-and-big-debts/articleshow/104484292.cms</guid></item><item><title>习近平对弗拉基米尔·普京的赌博会得到回报吗？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-russia-relations-will-xi-jinpings-gamble-on-vladimir-putin-pay-off/articleshow/104484083.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104484083.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京抵达北京与中国国家主席习近平举行会晤。由于西方制裁，俄罗斯越来越依赖中国的贸易和经济支持，预计两位领导人将讨论两国不断发展的经济关系。然而，有人担心中国没有从两国关系中获得足够的利益，而普京正在成为习近平的负担。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 03:54:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-russia-relations-will-xi-jinpings-gamble-on-vladimir-putin-pay-off/articleshow/104484083.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>